"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?5/4/5188?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Parkinson disease symptoms and diagnosis (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
